Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:06.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:17.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:35.63,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:41.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:48.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:53.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:55.32,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.34,0:01:03.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.43,0:01:12.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.85,0:01:16.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.40,0:01:21.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.99,0:01:28.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:34.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:39.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.42,0:01:41.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.67,0:01:45.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:49.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:50.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.68,0:01:52.37,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.73,0:01:57.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:59.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.44,0:02:01.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.53,0:02:05.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.91,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:21.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.42,0:02:25.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:32.82,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.84,0:02:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Promise from a Distant Day!\NThe Pirates' Song and a Small Whale!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure we should leave Perona?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take someone we can't find.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! Where in the world did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! Okay, you can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:04:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lift your invisibility power!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.93,0:04:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free and clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was terrified we'd get \Ncaught the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.90,0:04:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never did find out what brought\NTyrant Kuma to Thriller Bark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that, Absalom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tyrant Kuma came to tell us the name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the successor to the\Nformer Warlord, Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.12,0:04:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His successor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but that's not the important part.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The successor is a man called Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pulled a truly nasty stunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Read that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.55,0:04:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Fire Fist Ace, 2nd Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been imprisoned in Impel Down"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's well known that Ace is\None of Whitebeard's top dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.31,0:04:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government just got\Ntheir hands on a powerful card.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.64,0:04:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on how they play it,\Nthis could completely change the Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a serious situation on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time for Moria-sama\Nto be dead to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see where you're coming from,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm more interested... in finding a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Bring me a corpse that turns you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna marry a living woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"One Day After Defeating Moria"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.88,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,everyone slept all day in that courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.87,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sure. We were up all the\Nprevious night fighting like mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nibble on some cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese doesn't cut it!\NCheese doesn't energize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.11,0:05:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then start hauling the ingredients\NI need to the courtyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.03,0:05:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the members of the Victim\NAssociation don't want to budge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're eating over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.07,0:05:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is just so happy to see\Nthe sun for the first time in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.91,0:05:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are crying tears \Nof joy while sunbathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.87,0:05:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did all of that energy come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:05:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so weird! It's a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have enough food?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a mountain of additional food
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Non top of everything that was stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who did that. There are\Nsome nice people out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they even loaded your ship\Nwith all of this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even assuming it was Christmas,\Nthis is far too generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bliss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a glass armband!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I claim this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you know what'll happen\Nif you take any of the treasure...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can have it! There aren't any gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is that how this works? Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have a single\Npiece of treasure for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wouldn't take treasure from\Nthe people who saved us, Namizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.80,0:06:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a nice knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! This is out. \NIt's studded with gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It popped right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is Namizo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, this is rather strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some odd reason, I don't feel\Nlike this is the first time we've met.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance, are you Lola?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Did I tell you my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Lola...? Wh-Whoa, wait! Just a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That boar zombie was her...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be confused, huh? \NI'll fill you in later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, take this. It's \Nmy way of thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Are you sure? You're thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami gave away some of our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on ahead. Is this everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.35,0:07:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A storm? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light is seeping into my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought food!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you told us, we would have carried it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe shouldn't let our savior work!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Zoro up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He needs absolute rest, \Nso he's in the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought the stuff you asked for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen Zoro so badly hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He nearly lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think something must have happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...while we were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.29,0:08:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I sincerely doubt \Nthat man simply left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's strange how Luffy\Nis bursting with energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's up with that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I saw what went down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what happened from beginning to end!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you the dirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fill you in on what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.98,0:09:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! No, wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold up!\N--Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.19,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why?! You were pretty cool yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.54,0:09:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were like, "Instead of the\Nswordsman's life, take mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now start talking. What happened afterwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.95,0:09:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know what happened\Nafter I blacked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.30,0:09:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Warlord had yet \Nanother shocking ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pressed his paw against Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.93,0:09:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It repelled all of the "damage"\Nthat Straw Hat had taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His damage...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like a bubble of agony. And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to take his place,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take all of his pain and \Nsuffering unto yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:10:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be impossible for you to survive\Nwhen you are already on the brink of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a small taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.55,0:10:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the swordsman started\Nscreaming bloody murder
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when he touched a small portion of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but I \Nthought he was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.48,0:10:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what makes it so touching!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seriously made me cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That explains why Luffy is\Ndoing well while Zoro is bedridden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did all of this blood come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing happened...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's tell everyone\Nabout the Straw Hats' heroic story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm itching to tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be insensitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't risk his life out of\Na desire to earn our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What would happen if they learned that\NLuffy's pain hurt a friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how badly are you \Ndying to tell everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't tell them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're killing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.30,0:11:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th... Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys are super cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their captain is so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that explains it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you acting like you knew\Nwhat happened? What did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask such an insensitive question.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.50,0:12:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that matters is that everyone is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wanna tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep that manly heroic story to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.59,0:12:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the food!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delish! I've never eaten \Nsuch good food before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here! Try this! This!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's been years since\Nwe've eaten a decent meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cooked up a storm! \NDon't let it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think I get to eat your cooking again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.75,0:12:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This really is lip-smacking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I have any lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:13:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to shut up and eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That skeleton is hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But honestly--oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.85,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After eating until I was full\Nboth yesterday and today,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.56,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have gained weight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.11,0:13:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even though I'm a skeleton!"\NI can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, you rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.61,0:13:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come that skeleton is able to talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's a hoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a clever skeleton, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.08,0:13:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you able to move around?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.08,0:13:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it doesn't really matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, dinner!\N--Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.55,0:13:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Oh, baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.54,0:13:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dinner!\N--Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't have a toast\Nand it still turned into a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.56,0:13:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sleeping right through all this noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here he's the toughest guy in the crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chopper! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--This is for Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now drink away!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give it to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?! This will fix Zoro\Nright up, since it's his favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What type of treatment is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.43,0:14:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work? Then how about meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.85,0:14:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay. I'll gladly accept\Nyour sentiment alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only your sentiment!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a piano in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I thought you only played the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can play most instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'd like to touch on \Nan earlier conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I also saw what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was greatly moved by what you two did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it wonderful to have comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't include me in that.\NI merely made a fool of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you bore the same resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.53,0:15:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to pick a song?\NI'll take a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? I can request anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait, didn't you just ask for a request?!\N--♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Yo-ho ho ho, yo-ho ho ho ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We're on our way... ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ ...to deliver Bink's booze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail leisurely with the sea breeze ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Sail with the waves ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.83,0:16:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ The setting sun romps about\Non the other side of the tide ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ A ring of birds in the sky sing ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Bid farewell to the port\Nof the weaving village ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ As we set sail, we \Nshall sing heartily ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ Silver and gold waves \Nturn into ocean spray ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,♪ We are off, bound for \Nthe ends of the ocean ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bink's Booze." I thought\NI recognized the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.52,0:16:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee! Yahoo! Keep it going!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Brook! I know this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shanks and the guys used to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. A long time ago,\Nall of the pirates would sing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They sang it in good times and bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're gonna join our crew now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you've got your shadow back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can hit the seas without\Nfear of the sun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.85,0:18:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About that. There was one thing\NI neglected to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.15,0:18:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.58,0:18:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised one of my comrades something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.48,0:18:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must tend to that first \Nor I will lose face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're talking \Nabout Laboon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about it. \NFranky and Robin told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.17,0:18:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.29,0:18:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the name of the whale.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.34,0:18:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is at a certain cape--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Brook! We met Laboon\Nat Twin Cape. Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already knew that Laboon
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.56,0:18:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had been waiting there for his friends
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to return for the past fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Skeleton, what's wrong?\NThe tempo is getting slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the symbol of\Nour promise to fight again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we come back, don't remove that\Nmark by hitting your head. Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, whale! I'm leaving now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.12,0:19:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, was I ever surprised when I learned\Nthat you're the surviving member
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.54,0:19:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the band of pirates he's been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.30,0:20:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you still remember your promise to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Laboon would be thrilled if he knew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm shocked! This is so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true? Did you actually meet Laboon?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.40,0:20:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though fifty years have passed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon is still waiting for us at that cape?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling the truth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.71,0:20:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.12,0:20:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also bore witness.\NWe saw him with our own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he well?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was as big as a mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we left him, the cutie \Nwas about the size of a boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had a stubborn streak, but he loved music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.89,0:20:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...picture him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.54,0:21:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never been this happy in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that whale come from?\NIt's following our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must have gotten separated from its pod.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.70,0:21:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The poor thing. The ocean is a big place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.37,0:21:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks sad. Well, it's still just a calf.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.55,0:22:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yorkie, why don't we play a song?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great idea, Brook! Hey, everyone!\NGrab your instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's show him what the \NRumbar Pirates that make
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.32,0:22:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,crying children laugh are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.69,0:22:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laboon, you are our dear comrade!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.38,0:23:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we can't take you with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.18,0:23:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Line is so dangerous,\Nwe want you to wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.92,0:23:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will swing around the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear we will come back\Nto this cape to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.89,0:23:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.51,0:23:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Brook's Past! A Sad Farewell\Nwith His Cheerful Comrade!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.01,0:23:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
